    ">
        <h1 style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 3rem; color: #0d6efd;">Welcome to Metric System</h1>
        <p class="lead" style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #000;">Easily convert from British system to international metric system.</p>
    </div>
